author: Kevin Goddard
title: Casanova - Don't Run (Remix) Feat. Fabolous, Dave East, Young M.A & Don Q
text:
0 NOT FEELING IT 0 MAKE IT STOP Brooklyn's Casanova calls on Dave East, Young M.A., Fabolous, & Don Q for his remix to “Don’t Run.” 
Brooklyn rapper Casanova, who was once cell-mates with A$AP Rocky at Rikers Island , has been teasing fans of an upcoming remix to his “Don’t Run” single featuring Fabolous , Young MA, Dave East & Don Q on twitter recently, and now it’s surfaced after being premiered on NYC radios Tuesday night. 
Listen as each New York spitter rep their boroughs to the fullest & lay down some respective bars over production from the NY Bangers. Who had the best verse? (Music video already shot & on the way as well) 
Quotable Lyrics: 
I guess time is money and if being broke is a joke Ya’ll never find us funny I’m on a thousand, the shit you on is lousy So your shorty let me beat her like Ronda Rousey 
- Fab
